Youth drawn from the North Rift region who were discharged with the responsibility of digitizing birth and death certificates during the extension of huduma number exercise last year are now demanding their full pay from the government .speaking at Kapsoya DC grounds, Eldoret East civil registry office in Uasin Gishu county, they called upon interior cabinet secretary DR Fred Matiangi to move          with speed and intervene in the matter. They claim that their efforts to seek audience with relevant authorities have so far proven futile